title: Mouth to Mouth with Katherine Bailess (aka Erica Marsh) • EP214
itunes:title: Mouth to Mouth with Katherine Bailess (aka Erica Marsh) • EP214
description:
Katherine Bailess (Erica Marsh) joins The Drama Queens this week as Brooke and Erica clash on screen in the race to win Student Council President.


Can you guess what movie Katherine and Joy co-starred in prior to OTH?! AND which Tree Hill character Katherine originally auditioned for?


This episode give us what we want as things hear up between Jake and Peyton! Tune in to hear every detail of our favorite on screen duo.
